entry.string: echo "Building the project..." mvn clean package -DskipTests
echo "Running unit and integration tests..." mvn clean verify -DskipTests=false

echo "Logging in to Docker Hub..." echo "$DOCKER_PASSWORD" | docker login -u "$DOCKER_USERNAME" --password-stdin
echo "Building and pushing Docker images..." docker-compose -f compose.yml build docker-compose -f compose.yml push
echo "Logout from Docker Hub..." docker logout
